Game class
----------

This event operates on an instance of the [game
class](Game_class "Game class") type {{{gameclass}}}

Description
-----------

Line drawing for debug visualization.

Usage
-----

*void* debugLine( *vector* **color** , *vector* **start** , *vector*
**end** , *float* **lifetime** )

Parameters
----------

-   [color] - The color to draw the line.
-   [start] - The starting point of the line.
-   [end] - The ending point of the line.
-   [lifetime] - The duration to display the line.

